                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9822" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1484</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1549 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“金通灵”的幻灭：六年财务造假的华丽谢幕</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The disillusionment of &quot;golden spirit&quot;: the gorgeous end of six years of financial fraud</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">冷昕，徐莹莹，蔡逸群</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金通灵科技集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金通灵；财务造假；虚构收入；中介机构责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Jin Tongling; Financial fraud; Fictitious income; Intermediary liability</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在经济增速放缓与考核指标刚性的双重压力下，个别企业为了应对政绩考核或退市风险，以粉饰财务数据为目的，使用虚构交易、关联方协同等造假手段虚增利润。金通灵曾被誉为中国高端装备制造业的“明日之星”，然而2023年11月，证监会曝光其连续6年存在财务造假行为，虚增收入超10亿元。同年12月，中国证监会对金通灵及其负责人、负责审计的大华会计师事务所、保荐机构华西证券等均进行了相应处罚。本案例以金通灵财务造假事件作为警示样本，通过对该案例的梳理引导学生分析财务造假的动因、手段与危害，提升学生对会计职业道德等商业伦理的认知，强调作为注册会计师事务所等相关从业人员的职业勤勉与诚信建设的重要性。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Under the dual pressure of slowing economic growth and rigid assessment indicators, individual enterprises, in order to cope with the risk of performance appraisal or delisting, use fictitious transactions, related party collaboration and other fraudulent means to falsely increase profits for the purpose of whitewashing financial data. Jin Tongling was once known as the &quot;star of tomorrow&quot; in China&#39;s high-end equipment manufacturing industry. However, in November 2023, the CSRC exposed its financial fraud for six consecutive years, and its inflated income exceeded 1 billion yuan. In December of the same year, China Securities Regulatory Commission imposed corresponding penalties on Jin Tongling and its responsible person, Dahua Certified Public Accountants, the sponsor institution Huaxi Securities, etc. This case takes Jin Tongling&#39;s financial fraud as a warning sample. By combing the case, it guides students to analyze the motivation, means and harm of financial fraud, enhances students&#39; understanding of business ethics such as accounting professional ethics, and emphasizes the importance of professional diligence and integrity construction as a certified public accounting firm and other related practitioners.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《审计理论与实务》、《商业伦理与会计职业道德》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">GONE理论；财务舞弊的概念及手段；中介机构责任；商业伦理；会计职业道德</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
